        "title": "创业资金：卑诗各行业补助金申请",
        "excerpt":"创业补助金其实并不多，而且申请程序大都比较繁杂，耗时耗力。以下是卑诗省不同行业相对有针对性的一些补助金项目，大家可以根据自己所处的行业和需求进行选择。   农业（Agriculture Grants）      Agriculture Environment Initiatives   Investment Agriculture Foundation   BC Buy local program   Dairy Processing Investment Fund   商业与艺术（Grants for Business and the Arts）      Launch Online Grant   Canada United Small Business Relief Fund   UBCO Arts Career Apprenticeship program   Beekeeping Grant: Bee BC Program   Strategic Innovation Fund   Venture Capital Programs   Employee Share Ownership Program   Labour Sponsored Funds Program   The British Columbia Arts Council   ARTS BC   Canada Council for the Arts Grants   City of Vancouver Cultural Services, Grants, Awards &amp; Support Programs   Northern Development Competitiveness Consulting Rebate    Canada Periodical Fund   Film Incentive BC Tax Credit   Columbia Basin Trust Arts and Culture Grants   Production Services Tax Credit   环境（Grants for Environmental Initiatives）      Canada’s funding programs for the Environment and Climate Change   Northern Industries Innovation Fund   Sustainable Development Tech Fund   Program of Energy Research and Development (PERD)   Climate Action Fund   出口（Export Support Grants）      CanExport Grant   Canadian International Innovation Program   科研创新（Research and Technology Grants）      Innovation, Science and Economic Development Canada   National Research Council Canada – Industrial Research Assistance Program (IRAP)   Mitacs   贸易（Trades Grants）      Government of Canada support for apprentices   Apprenticeship Incentive Grant   Apprenticeship Completion Grant   Women in Trades Training   工资补贴（Grants for Wage Subsidies）      Province of BC – Targeted Wage Subsidies employment program   Province of BC – Job Creation Partnerships employment program   Province of BC – Labour Market Partnerships employment program   Douglas College – Career Focus Wage Subsidy Program   Get Youth Working Program   Connect Canada Internship    Tech Co-op Grant from Innovate BC   Innovate BC Innovator Skills Initiative (ISI) Grant   New Ventures BC – up to $10,000 student grant program   YMCA of Greater Vancouver Youth Employment Wage Subsidy    其它 (Other Grants)      NEW Small and Medium Sized Business Recovery Grant   Windmill Microlending Program   BMO Celebrating Women Grant   Enabling Accessibility Fund   StartUp Canada Women Founders Fund for Women-led STEM companies   Canada-BC Job Grant   Federal Government – Employee / Skills Subsidy or Grant Programs   Vancouver Foundation Grants  ","categories": ["创业"],
